            . I am in the service of Thomas Edge, a <rs id="t18270215-217-viclabel1165" type="occupation">gas apparatus maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270215-217-victim1168 t18270215-217-viclabel1165"></join>, of Westminster - the prisoner was in his employ. On the 15th of February I placed myself in the store-room, and saw the prisoner look into a room where this brass laid - he unlocked the door, went in, and took out three pigs of brass in his arms - I had marked Edge's name on them - he was secured putting it into his bosom; he earned 22s. a week.</p>
               <p>
            
